[[ch04-overview-infinity-and-beyond]]
== Overview: Infinity And Beyond

To Infinity! And Beyond!

Irreni scales to infinity and beyond! Let's dicuss!

I suppose I should give a sense of what is meant by the use of the word "scale". In computer science the world scale does mean growth. To say Irreni scales to infinity does mean Irreni does grow to infinity. However, the world scale also means "at every size". In other words that design scale works at size 1, 10, 100, 1,000 ... A design that scales works at any size. In this chapter we are going to look at both size one and size infinity. Irreni scales to any size. Irreni can shrink as well as expand size.

Irreni scales infinitely and to any size big or small using one fundamental principle: all growth is horizontal.

Imagine there is a human society, the Spacies, that only exists on spaceships. Spacies have perfected building self-contained spaceships for human living. Ships have everything for those on board to live out a natural life. Power, food, water, medicine, dental, living quarters, and so on provide for life cradle to space grave. Further imagine that they realized the best way to survive is if all the ships had the same structural design. In other words these ships all supported the same population size.

A single ship design allows all the ships in the fleet to interchange parts. Manufacturing is simplified to one set of designs.

Let's say the Spacies have a population of nine billion. The spaceship size is thirty people. This means there are 300 million ships. Thirty may seem too small. However the small size is intended to withstand disaster optimally.

Imagine a disaster occurs where some rogue asteroid tears through the fleet killing millions. Small ships have the best chance to change course at the last minute. Small ships minimize impact damage to approximate just the path the rogue asteroid takes. After the disaster all damaged ships have parts from millions of other ships to repair with or to use as lifeboats.

Now imagine the Spacies exist millions of years in the future. Over millions of years they have kept to the same perfected small design. The Spacies have colonized large portions of Milky Way. Imagine a fleet of Spacie ships meet that are hundreds of thousands of years old meet up with the latest versions. The spaceships are still the same size. The parts are still interchangeable. The fleet can expand and shrink seamlessly.

This is horizontal growth. Horizontal growth expands to fill the Universe or survives natural disasters the most. Horizontal growth expands in both time and space dimensions with equal success.

Now further imagine the Spacies have designed their spaceships to land on new planets and colonize them using the spaceship that flew through space. The spaceships land on solid ground and like a camper just roll out various ground features. Otherwise day-to-day life for the thirty people on the ship remains the same.

The Spacies have the most resilient and robust design for survival until the end of the Universe. Further, if we have any chance of stopping the expansion of the Universe technically in a trillion years or so then we'll need to populate as much of the Universe as possible.


First lesson of infinite scale design is simplicity to the maximum extent possible is required. The simplicity provides resilience and robustness when disasters occur. Maximally complex designs scale the least.

One can intuitively understand that more complexity means more fragility by thinking about a game, Jenga. Jenga is a game where blocks of rectangular wood blocks are stacked. Blocks are removed until the structure collapses. One block removed collapses the entire structure. This is not possible with horizontal growth. Spread out all the blocks on the table. Remove one then only that block fails. All the others remain functional.

The US is going to completely collapse because it is complex. At some point one more Jenga block is going to be removed and the entire thing will collapse. Jenga in this case is corruption. The rich are robbing the US blind with a fever pitch. The rich are stealing everything that isn't bolted down and they are loosening the bolts. They are playing Jenga in that they are all trying to remove blocks before the entire system collapses. This type of corruption is possible because the US society design is vertical and doesn't scale.

Irreni design is a Spacies design. However, technology doesn't exist today to live in space, only on Earth. So our fixed size "ships" are "Earthships" called MGOs, mesh/micro governing organizations. When Irreni Society covers everyone on Earth there will be 300 million MGOs where each MGO houses thirty people. The rogue asteroid disaster design benefits still apply. Horizontal design is the most robust design and the maximal number of humans will survive a rogue asteroid. Today our complex large scale societies are so fragile that such an asteroid would bring with it total social collapse killing billions that would not die in horizontal designs.

Horizontal design provides new opportunities in addition to replace vertical, Old Democracy designs of today.

Climate change is here to stay. The Earth is going to heat up. Perhaps Stone Age people would react better than we are today in that they would seek caves to live in. Horizontal MGOs could begin designing new Earthships to survive underground in caves. We could then start moving ever larger number of people underground, thirty people at a time.

This same design capability expands to living underwater.

Current designs by futurists posit that everyone should move to large cities. Now imagine a pandemic or asteroid hit that city. Pandemic technology in large cities would necessarily be much more complex than for MGOs.

Now is a good time to introduce the survival requirements for the horizontal MGO unit.

Every MGO is required to have on hand at all times one year's worth of supply of food, water, and power. This seems odd to us today but it isn't really once you settle in on it.

Today, we all go grocery shopping weekly to restock. Irreni also will have weekly grocery shopping. However the supplies will be to restock the year's supply instead of using immediately. This is akin to getting off of living paycheck-to-paycheck to living on a savings of one year's money supply.

The year's supply of survival goods accomplishes two design requirements:

1. Survival
2. Social power, aka political power in today's parlance.

Survival is illustrated by imagining the world in 2020 was horizontal and not vertical society. Everyone lives in an MGO. The Covid pandemic hits. Every MGO has one year's supply of survival goods on hand. MGOs are sovereign. This means each MGO can decide to isolate up to one year with minimal penalty except forgoing perishables and such.

But it gets better. MGOs work remotely as design. Isolation is built into horizontal design. Each MGO has its own medical personnel and medical bay to handle vaccinations, etc. MGOs have all the infrastructure to manage healthcare at the MGO scale. Of course projects that require large numbers of people to work outside the MGOs will be scaled back or halted.

People would still die in a pandemic like Covid in horizontal society. However, MGOs would provide the highest survival-ability rates compared to nations today.

Social power is also illustrated with the pandemic as well. Irreni replaces governments with projects. In the future large scale human efforts in medicine will be done in projects. MGOs that want vaccines can attach themselves to such projects as either labor working on the project or as trade only for the vaccine. The MGO isolation design being horizontal means the 90% herd immunization can be avoided by isolating MGOs that don't vaccinate. MGOs that don't vaccinate are simply banned from providing workers to projects that have vaccinated workers.

Horizontal society design is ideology neutral. MGOs of differing ideologies co-exist with natural isolation boundaries. This is social power.

Let's talk about tyranny, oppression and authoritarianism. You know, Christian Nationalism.

Irreni is not a Utopian design. Irreni is an engineering design of scale. Any ideology is allowed because Irreni is about functions provided by engineering.

The best way to think about Christian Nationalism and Irreni design is the same as with survival disaster. Irreni is designed to be robust and resilient in the face of tyranny and oppression and minimize the destruction caused. When a MAGA movement materializes in an Irreni world then the impact will be minimized.

Imagine MAGA takes off in a horizontal society. First they would withdraw from MGO society and build a vertical society of patriarchy/hierarchy. Perhaps they then go so far as to declare war on MGOs and start bombing killing, raping and plundering like in Gaza, Lebanon, or Iran today. The people of Gaza, Lebanon and Iran live at the mercy of the vertical government today. Not so in an MGO world. Each MGO of size thirty people is sovereign. This means new alliances can be built immediately at scale to meet any such threat. The MGOs in what is Gaza, Lebanon, and Iran today would  have a year's supply of survival goods on hand.

Irreni is a voluntary design. This means individual scan withdraw and join at any time. It also means MGOs can withdraw and join at any time.

An all voluntary design scales the best. Why? Because the horizontal design must, by design, be the most attractive possible in order to grow and maintain size.

Irreni attracts everyone via project zero. Project zero is management. Projects require all member MGOs treat their members with dignity in order to join a project. MGOs are allowed to have any ideology and any governing structure, including monarchy and theocracy that are maligned today. This is because Irreni is social engineering not social ideology. Irreni requires responsibilities and not rights. MGOs are responsible for educating, feeding, and otherwise being responsible with all MGO members. If any MGO harms and oppresses members they are not allowed to join projects based on member treatment requirements. 

The largest project of MGO members will have the least requirements across all ideologies of MGOs and this is called project zero. Project zero designates the least set of responsibilities required for all its members: education, health, and opportunity. When an MGO meets all these standards then they are allowed to join project zero. Then the MGO can join any other project with stricter human management requirements along ideological lines for trade and labor.

Projects can be viewed somewhat like nations within the United Nations. It is expected that there will be many, many projects in Irreni. These projects will nest and where the largest MGO sizes will loosen MGO member requirements to form ever larger groups in order to address larger project requirements such as climate change. The largest management project that contains the most MGOs is project zero. Project zero then is a set of least common requirements that MGOs agree upon across all the ideologies that MGO management projects adhere to.

This system of nested projects is the most robust possible. Projects can scale from size two MGOS to the largest possible.

One other design feature of Irreni engineering that ensures scalability is that project contracts only last a maximum of five years. One way to image this is to imagine the US Constitution was written to include a "vote of no confidence" for the entire government to be taken every five years. Now, one can imagine that this might happen quite regularly. So, in order to prevent complete collapse what would happen is the project contract called the Constitution is constantly undergoing revisions. Whenever a vote of no confidence succeeds then a new Constitution that has already been approved is now put into place.

Irreni design requires project contracts to expire every five years maximum. Project contracts can have shorter durations. Various ideologies are always going to fight over ideological boundaries. Realize the initial project contract was agreed upon only when all its members approved. This means that the starting point was after approval of all things. Renewal of an expired contract then could mean many things. The size of the project gets smaller as MGOs withdraw on ideological grounds. The requirements of the project itself get smaller on ideological grounds. Both scenarios can happen where the MGO size gets smaller and the requirements get smaller. And, of course, the project just may just expire.

This horizontal design allows different competing ideologies fertile ground to compete maximally. It is engineering and not ideology itself.

Ideologies do exist that demand tyranny and oppression of all humans. Those ideologies will necessarily be destroyed in war. Such ideologies are called uncooperative ideologies. They refuse to cooperate with any other ideology. Irreni only supports cooperative ideologies.

So the horizontal design engineering of Irreni not only applies to MGO design but project design where projects have to be renewed every five years. This is somewhat analogous to the checks-and-balances of the US Constitution today where ideologies are balanced on State and Federal ideological lines. That is too coarse of granularity though. In Irreni there can be an unlimited number of projects and they can scale from size two MGOS to all the MGOs if possible.

Weird. As I said in the last chapter Irreni is weird in that it scales to infinity and beyond. Irreni is still a democracy in that it is of the people, by the people, and for the people. Each MGO has its own ideology. The principle of one person, one vote can apply within the MGO itself although MGOs are free to choose any governing structure they want, including monarchy. They just won't be able to join projects unless their treatment of MGO members meet the responsibility requirements of treatment by project contracts. The project contract that contains the largest number of MGOs is called project zero.

Over time I expect that ever larger groups of MGOs will join project zero first since it has the least requirements and most MGO members. Then they will join more restrictive management of finer granularity ideology as they see fit.

Maximum effort!

To infinity and beyond!
